thread.title: TV | Clean Break

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | Clean Break
text: Final part in this nail-biting Irish drama tonight sees the wall of silence surrounding the Rane kidnapping start to break down. Frank has just lost it altogether and is determined to bring down those plotting against him, regardless of who gets in his way. While Jenny's curiousity leads her to stumbling across some crucial information that may well put her in great danger. Here's hoping there will be some sort of satisfying resolution to it all though, and RTE don't pull an 'Amber' on us.
